lead_paragraph: France, who have earned a reputation for leaving it late at this European Championship, would be well-advised to wake up early when they face Iceland for a place in the semi-finals, veteran defender Patrice Evra warned on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Wake Up France! Iceland Next, Says Evra
headline.main: Wake Up France! Iceland Next, Says Evra
